# Data Talk - Project Analysis

> Generated: 2026-04-02  
> Scope: Full-system analysis after cleanup and session-isolation refactor

---

## 1. Executive Summary

Data Talk is a Flask + Supabase + Gemini application that supports:

1. Authenticated dataset upload and preview.
2. Chat-based analysis with SSE phase streaming.
3. Pinning generated charts into a dashboard.
4. Persistent multi-session conversation history per user.

The latest refactor shifted the product in three important ways:

1. File-library management was removed end-to-end.
2. Dashboard state is now session-scoped so each conversation has its own visualization canvas.
3. A dedicated profile settings page and API flow were added.

Operational constraints now include a strict 1MB upload limit on both frontend and backend.

